dronium ion. The structure of hydrate shows a carbon bonded to a pink hydroxyl group at the top; the carbon shows an open dash and an open wedge bond on the left the carbon is also bonded to a blue hydroxyl group on the right.">
    <image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/OChem_19_05_003.jpg"/>
